```
ResolvNow/
├── server.js                  ← Entry point: DNS override → DB → Seed → Middleware → Routes
├── package.json               ← Dependencies & scripts
├── .env                       ← Environment variables (ไม่ commit)
│
├── config/                    ← ไฟล์ตั้งค่าทั้งหมด
│   ├── db.js                  ← MongoDB connection (IPv4, Google DNS)
│   ├── seed.js                ← Auto-seed admin + technicians + citizen
│   ├── cloudinary.js          ← Cloudinary + multer storage config
│   ├── mailer.js              ← Nodemailer Gmail OTP sender
│   └── lineNotify.js          ← LINE Messaging API push functions
│
├── models/                    ← Mongoose schemas
│   ├── User.js                ← ผู้ใช้ (citizen / technician / admin)
│   ├── Ticket.js              ← เรื่องร้องเรียน
│   ├── HelpRequest.js         ← คำขอช่วยเหลือระหว่างช่าง
│   ├── Comment.js             ← ความคิดเห็นใน ticket
│   └── Counter.js             ← Auto-increment (TKT-001, HELP-001)
│
├── routes/                    ← Express router files
│   ├── auth.js                ← /api/auth — login, register, OTP, LINE link
│   ├── tickets.js             ← /api/tickets — CRUD, assign, upload, rating
│   ├── technicians.js         ← /api/technicians — ดึงรายชื่อช่าง
│   ├── helpRequests.js        ← /api/help-requests — ขอช่วยเหลือ
│   ├── ai.js                  ← /api/ai — วิเคราะห์ความเร่งด่วน
│   └── lineAuth.js            ← /auth/line — LINE OAuth callback
│
├── data/
│   └── store.js               ← otpStore (in-memory Map), STATUSES, DEPT_MAP
│
└── public/                    ← Static files (SPA)
    ├── index.html             ← Single HTML file — ทุก section/modal
    ├── css/
    │   ├── style.css          ← Main stylesheet
    │   └── animations.css     ← Splash, page-enter, 3D transitions
    ├── js/
    │   ├── ui.js              ← Shared helpers, toast, badges, clock
    │   ├── app.js             ← Global state, enterApp(), session resume
    │   ├── auth.js            ← Login, register, OTP, LINE linking
    │   ├── admin.js           ← Admin dashboard, pie chart, queue
    │   ├── citizen.js         ← Citizen ticket form, GPS, file upload
    │   └── technician.js      ← Tech mission view, before/after upload
    └── uploads/               ← Local image fallback (ถ้าไม่มี Cloudinary)
```

