## 14. Deployment Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Render["☁️ Render.com"]
        WebService["Web Service<br/>Node.js 18+"]
        EnvVars["Environment Variables<br/>(13 keys)"]
    end

    subgraph MongoDB_Atlas["🍃 MongoDB Atlas"]
        Cluster["Cluster: resolvenow<br/>Region: Auto"]
        DB["Database: resolvenow"]
    end

    subgraph Cloudinary_CDN["☁️ Cloudinary"]
        Images["Folder: resolvenow/<br/>Auto-optimized images"]
    end

    WebService -->|mongoose| Cluster
    WebService -->|multer-storage-cloudinary| Images
    EnvVars -.->|config| WebService

    Users["👥 Users"] -->|HTTPS| WebService
    WebService -->|HTTPS| LINE_Platform["💚 LINE"]
    WebService -->|SMTP| Gmail["📧 Gmail"]
    WebService -->|HTTPS| Anthropic["🤖 Claude"]
```

### 14.1 DNS Override

```javascript
// server.js — บรรทัดแรกสุด ก่อน require ใดๆ
require('dns').setServers(['8.8.8.8', '8.8.4.4', '1.1.1.1']);
```

> [!WARNING]
> จำเป็นต้อง override DNS เพราะ ISP/network บางแห่ง block MongoDB Atlas SRV records ทำให้เชื่อมต่อ database ไม่ได้

### 14.2 Environment Variables

| Variable | Service | คำอธิบาย |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `MONGODB_URI` | MongoDB Atlas | Connection string |
| `MAIL_USER` | Gmail | Email สำหรับส่ง OTP |
| `MAIL_PASS` | Gmail | App Password (ไม่ใช่ password จริง) |
| `LINE_CHANNEL_TOKEN` | LINE | Messaging API access token |
| `LINE_ADMIN_USER_ID` | LINE | User ID ของ admin (รับ notification) |
| `LINE_LOGIN_CLIENT_ID` | LINE | LINE Login Channel ID |
| `LINE_LOGIN_CLIENT_SECRET` | LINE | LINE Login Channel Secret |
| `LINE_LOGIN_CALLBACK_URL` | LINE | OAuth callback URL |
| `CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME` | Cloudinary | Cloud name |
| `CLOUDINARY_API_KEY` | Cloudinary | API Key |
| `CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET` | Cloudinary | API Secret |
| `BASE_URL` | General | URL ของเว็บ (สำหรับ redirect, image URL) |
| `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` | Anthropic | Claude AI API Key |

